1
00:00:06,656 --> 00:00:11,904
 ♫ I still remember ♫ 

2
00:00:11,904 --> 00:00:15,518
 ♫ Your flickering gaze ♫ 

3
00:00:15,518 --> 00:00:17,303
 ♫ With a sense of excitement ♫ 

4
00:00:17,303 --> 00:00:20,832
 ♫ You vowed eternal love ♫ 

5
00:00:20,832 --> 00:00:25,984
 ♫ But over time, you've forgotten ♫ 

6
00:00:25,984 --> 00:00:31,232
 ♫ Promises drowned in life's twists ♫ 

7
00:00:31,232 --> 00:00:34,720
 ♫ Only memories remain like scattered fireworks ♫ 

8
00:00:34,720 --> 00:00:38,184
 ♫ When I turned to walk away ♫ 

9
00:00:38,184 --> 00:00:42,816
 ♫ If I could go back to the day we parted ♫ 

10
00:00:42,816 --> 00:00:49,088
 ♫ I'd never let go of your hand ♫ 

11
00:00:49,088 --> 00:00:53,824
 ♫ I cannot hide my feelings ♫ 

12
00:00:53,824 --> 00:00:55,904
 ♫ I'm about to be out of control ♫ 

13
00:00:55,904 --> 00:01:01,088
 ♫ As breathing turns weightless ♫ 

14
00:01:01,088 --> 00:01:03,104
 ♫ All I possess is drowned ♫ 

15
00:01:03,104 --> 00:01:06,072
 ♫ The me who still loves you deeply ♫ 

16
00:01:06,072 --> 00:01:07,968
 ♫ Has never changed ♫ 

17
00:01:07,968 --> 00:01:11,296
 ♫ If miracles could exist ♫ 

18
00:01:11,296 --> 00:01:13,351
 ♫ Promises would be kept ♫ 

19
00:01:13,351 --> 00:01:15,328
 ♫ Please remember ♫ 

20
00:01:15,328 --> 00:01:20,343
 ♫ The dream where you see me ♫ 

21
00:01:27,072 --> 00:01:29,952
 

22
00:01:29,952 --> 00:01:32,832
 

23
00:01:39,968 --> 00:01:41,088
Where is Ye Meng?

24
00:01:41,088 --> 00:01:43,040
She hasn't arrived yet.

25
00:01:45,540 --> 00:01:47,456
 

26
00:01:59,410 --> 00:02:01,930
Ye Meng's been kidnapped. Call the police.

27
00:02:37,170 --> 00:02:38,930
Where's Ye Meng?

28
00:02:38,930 --> 00:02:41,010
You came surprisingly fast.

29
00:02:47,370 --> 00:02:49,730
Do you realize what you're doing?

30
00:02:50,410 --> 00:02:52,730
You care about her quite a bit.

31
00:02:52,730 --> 00:02:54,850
But I don't care anymore.

32
00:02:54,850 --> 00:02:57,890
At worst, we all die together.

33
00:02:57,890 --> 00:02:59,890
Are you crazy?

34
00:03:01,250 --> 00:03:03,290
Yes, I am.

35
00:03:03,970 --> 00:03:07,050
Driven mad by all of you.

36
00:03:07,050 --> 00:03:09,970
Li Jin Yu, you've got some nerve.

37
00:03:09,970 --> 00:03:12,830
Colluding with your grandfather against me?

38
00:03:13,570 --> 00:03:16,610
You don't understand what Hanhai means to me.

39
00:03:16,610 --> 00:03:19,490
I built it with my happiness and lifeblood.

40
00:03:19,490 --> 00:03:21,530
You won't take it from me.

41
00:03:30,690 --> 00:03:33,090
Don't you just want my shares?

42
00:03:33,090 --> 00:03:35,170
I'll give them to you.

43
00:03:35,170 --> 00:03:37,410
You already hurt Ye Meng's mother.

44
00:03:37,410 --> 00:03:39,170
Don't harm Ye Meng anymore.

45
00:03:39,170 --> 00:03:42,112
That woman ruined my entire life.

46
00:03:42,112 --> 00:03:44,850
Who are you to judge me?

47
00:03:44,850 --> 00:03:46,720
Calm down.

48
00:03:49,530 --> 00:03:51,450
I'll sign right now.

49
00:04:03,850 --> 00:04:06,130
Don't cross me again.

50
00:04:11,490 --> 00:04:13,970
Ye Meng! Ye Meng!

51
00:04:29,370 --> 00:04:30,650
 We only have 

52
00:04:30,650 --> 00:04:32,490
 this one child. 

53
00:04:32,490 --> 00:04:35,690
 We want to give her the best. 

54
00:04:35,690 --> 00:04:38,370
 So after I had my daughter, 

55
00:04:38,370 --> 00:04:41,930
 I focused all my energy on her. 

56
00:04:53,690 --> 00:04:55,810
The real show is just beginning.

57
00:04:56,490 --> 00:04:58,570
Leaving so soon?

58
00:05:07,850 --> 00:05:09,970
Ye Meng! Wake up, Ye Meng!

59
00:05:09,970 --> 00:05:12,850
Wake up, Ye Meng!

60
00:05:26,870 --> 00:05:29,870
 This is the price of loyalty to Li Ling Bai. 

61
00:05:29,870 --> 00:05:31,450
 My current state proves it. 

62
00:05:31,450 --> 00:05:34,890
 Won't you leave yourself an escape route? 

63
00:05:34,890 --> 00:05:38,510
 I have money. Let me go. 

64
00:05:38,510 --> 00:05:40,810
 And I'll give it all to you. 

65
00:05:42,368 --> 00:05:46,330
Remember your promise.

66
00:05:55,330 --> 00:05:57,184
Ye Meng.

67
00:06:14,050 --> 00:06:16,050
Ye Meng, wake up.

68
00:06:42,250 --> 00:06:46,330
Ye Meng, wake up.

69
00:07:03,930 --> 00:07:06,090
I'm sorry.

70
00:07:06,090 --> 00:07:10,250
Blame your worthless mother.

71
00:08:16,370 --> 00:08:18,656
Ye Meng.

72
00:08:18,656 --> 00:08:20,810
Ye Meng, wake up. Ye Meng.

73
00:08:21,810 --> 00:08:26,170
Ye Meng, don't scare me like this.

74
00:08:26,810 --> 00:08:29,810
Ye Meng, stop frightening me.

75
00:08:30,432 --> 00:08:33,152
 ♫ Every time I look at you ♫ 

76
00:08:33,152 --> 00:08:34,592
 ♫ I want to get closer ♫ 

77
00:08:34,592 --> 00:08:37,408
 ♫ I'm unconsciously addicted ♫ 

78
00:08:37,408 --> 00:08:41,696
 ♫ To those inadvertent heartbeats ♫ 

79
00:08:41,696 --> 00:08:44,032
 ♫ How could I bear to forget ♫ 

80
00:08:44,032 --> 00:08:46,624
 ♫ If you understand my feelings ♫ 

81
00:08:46,624 --> 00:08:48,320
 ♫ I want to escape ♫ 

82
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:50,880
 ♫ Because I care too much ♫ 

83
00:08:50,880 --> 00:08:55,424
 ♫ For the courage I lost ♫ 

84
00:08:55,424 --> 00:08:58,560
 ♫ How can I pick it up ♫ 

85
00:08:58,560 --> 00:09:01,312
 ♫ Using my last bit of strength ♫ 

86
00:09:01,312 --> 00:09:05,024
 ♫ I'll embrace you ♫ 

87
00:09:05,024 --> 00:09:07,360
 ♫ Don't doubt ♫ 

88
00:09:34,148 --> 00:09:38,528
 

89
00:10:04,810 --> 00:10:06,850
Here to laugh at me?

90
00:10:09,730 --> 00:10:11,730
I'm here to tell you,

91
00:10:13,090 --> 00:10:15,770
don't worry about Li Zhuo Feng.

92
00:10:15,770 --> 00:10:18,370
When he's recovered enough,

93
00:10:18,370 --> 00:10:21,250
I'll take him back to Ningsui for Grandma.

94
00:10:25,330 --> 00:10:27,810
I haven't endured your pain,

95
00:10:27,810 --> 00:10:30,570
so I can't tell you to stop hating.

96
00:10:32,690 --> 00:10:35,250
But someone told me,

97
00:10:35,250 --> 00:10:37,890
"The world means you no harm."

98
00:10:39,010 --> 00:10:43,010
That's true for everyone.

99
00:10:49,570 --> 00:10:56,090
Pain makes the world seem dark.

100
00:11:07,010 --> 00:11:10,810
Want to hear my story?

101
00:11:17,050 --> 00:11:19,810
 My adoptive father took me abroad. 

102
00:11:20,810 --> 00:11:25,610
 His business partner Chen Guo Sheng drugged me. 

103
00:11:35,330 --> 00:11:39,370
 I was young and too scared to tell anyone. 

104
00:11:40,410 --> 00:11:43,810
 A month later, I got pregnant. 

105
00:11:47,650 --> 00:11:51,570
 I bravely told my adoptive father, 

106
00:11:51,570 --> 00:11:55,808
 but he forced me
to marry Chen Guo Sheng for profit. 

107
00:12:04,050 --> 00:12:09,410
So that's why you hate me.

108
00:12:18,090 --> 00:12:22,450
Why target Ye Meng's mother then?

109
00:12:27,170 --> 00:12:31,890
Her sin? Being too happy.

110
00:12:42,530 --> 00:12:44,512
 Bai? 

111
00:12:51,264 --> 00:12:56,256
 Years later, fate reunited us. 

112
00:12:56,256 --> 00:12:59,090
 We were best friends at the orphanage 

113
00:12:59,090 --> 00:13:02,490
 but later lived completely different lives. 

114
00:13:02,490 --> 00:13:04,970
 Bai, have some fruit. 

115
00:13:06,130 --> 00:13:10,610
 Seems you've done well for yourself. 

116
00:13:10,610 --> 00:13:14,250
 Just like that. I was just lucky. 

117
00:13:14,250 --> 00:13:18,210
 Actually, you've always been likable. 

118
00:13:18,970 --> 00:13:22,650
 I remember when my dad came to the orphanage, 

119
00:13:22,650 --> 00:13:24,608
 the first one he noticed was you. 

120
00:13:24,608 --> 00:13:25,824
 I like it. 

121
00:13:25,824 --> 00:13:28,890
 Alright, then you wait here for me. 

122
00:13:32,610 --> 00:13:36,610
 Shu Yi, are you leaving? 

123
00:13:36,610 --> 00:13:39,490
 Then I'll be all alone after this. 

124
00:13:40,690 --> 00:13:44,970
 I actually don't really want to go to Jiangbei. 

125
00:13:44,970 --> 00:13:47,210
 Don't you want to leave here badly? 

126
00:13:47,210 --> 00:13:49,210
 Take this. 

127
00:13:52,690 --> 00:13:57,850
 If you hadn't rejected him,
he probably wouldn't have adopted me. 

128
00:13:59,410 --> 00:14:04,810
 My life might have been completely different. 

129
00:14:04,810 --> 00:14:10,530
 To be honest,
I really wanted to say yes back then. 

130
00:14:13,010 --> 00:14:15,530
 Then why did you refuse? 

131
00:14:15,530 --> 00:14:19,410
 Because I saw how much you loved that teddy bear. 

132
00:14:19,410 --> 00:14:24,370
 And I promised
I wouldn't leave you alone at the orphanage. 

133
00:14:27,090 --> 00:14:30,570
 I hated her for giving me this life, 

134
00:14:30,570 --> 00:14:33,490
 so I began my revenge. 

135
00:14:34,730 --> 00:14:38,272
 Wang Xing Sheng, you're a liar! A fraud! 

136
00:14:38,272 --> 00:14:39,610
 I'm going to report you to the police. 

137
00:14:39,610 --> 00:14:40,770
 Go ahead. Report me. 

138
00:14:40,770 --> 00:14:44,210
 Then I'll tell the police you're my accomplice. 

139
00:14:44,210 --> 00:14:47,488
 Don't forget. You're the one
who took me to the orphanage. 

140
00:14:47,488 --> 00:14:50,240
 You're the reason why
those townspeople are putting their money in. 

141
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:52,730
 - You're an accomplice.
- No! You tricked me. 

142
00:14:52,730 --> 00:14:54,770
 I didn't cheat them-- 

143
00:14:54,770 --> 00:14:57,330
 Do you think they'll believe you? 

144
00:15:00,650 --> 00:15:02,170
 Don't you care most about your family's reputation 

145
00:15:02,170 --> 00:15:03,490
 and your precious daughter? 

146
00:15:03,490 --> 00:15:04,650
 If this gets out, 

147
00:15:04,650 --> 00:15:06,330
 they'll be ruined because of you. 

148
00:15:06,330 --> 00:15:07,850
 Your daughter is still in high school. 

149
00:15:07,850 --> 00:15:10,250
 You better keep your mouth shut. 

150
00:15:10,250 --> 00:15:12,850
 If I ever get caught, 

151
00:15:12,850 --> 00:15:15,610
 I'll drag you down with me. 

152
00:15:19,970 --> 00:15:21,250
I just wanted her

153
00:15:21,250 --> 00:15:23,930
to feel the same pain as me.

154
00:15:25,970 --> 00:15:30,930
I never thought she'd kill herself.

155
00:15:38,170 --> 00:15:40,530
 Give that money back to me. 

156
00:15:40,530 --> 00:15:45,610
 That money is the lifelong savings
of everyone at the orphanage. 

157
00:15:45,610 --> 00:15:50,690
 You don't know how important
this money is to my family. 

158
00:15:53,090 --> 00:15:56,130
 Did you ever think about
how I've lived these years? 

159
00:15:57,050 --> 00:16:00,610
 You arbitrarily swapped our lives. 

160
00:16:07,050 --> 00:16:09,730
 You threw me into hell, you know that? 

161
00:16:09,730 --> 00:16:14,810
 I thought I was doing what was best for you. 

162
00:16:16,930 --> 00:16:19,810
 How nice. For my own good. 

163
00:16:24,090 --> 00:16:26,048
 For my own good? 

164
00:16:30,210 --> 00:16:34,250
 For my own good? You think I live a good life? 

165
00:16:38,784 --> 00:16:41,024
 Don't be like this, Bai. 

166
00:16:43,450 --> 00:16:46,450
 Shu Yi, let me tell you. 

167
00:16:46,450 --> 00:16:51,530
 Your current happiness comes from my misery. 

168
00:16:51,530 --> 00:16:52,890
 I want everyone to know 

169
00:16:52,890 --> 00:16:55,210
 you're a despised fraud. 

170
00:16:55,210 --> 00:16:57,248
 I'll make your family and child 

171
00:16:57,248 --> 00:16:59,610
 live in shame because of you
for the rest of their lives. 

172
00:16:59,610 --> 00:17:01,970
 Don't be like this, Bai. 

173
00:17:01,970 --> 00:17:06,912
 I want you to feel all the pain I've endured. 

174
00:17:06,912 --> 00:17:10,144
 This is what you owe me. 

175
00:17:10,144 --> 00:17:13,330
 Bai, Bai. 

176
00:17:15,490 --> 00:17:17,610
 Bai! 

177
00:18:06,250 --> 00:18:11,890
 I know you hate me. 

178
00:18:13,650 --> 00:18:15,650
 I hate you, too. 

179
00:18:19,850 --> 00:18:24,770
In your most painful times,

180
00:18:26,690 --> 00:18:30,250
Ye Meng was there to hold you back.

181
00:18:36,450 --> 00:18:42,090
Actually, like you, I've had my moments of luck.

182
00:18:44,096 --> 00:18:45,530
 It's kicking. Feel here. 

183
00:18:45,530 --> 00:18:47,328
 Really? 

184
00:18:47,328 --> 00:18:48,736
 Oh, it really is. 

185
00:18:48,736 --> 00:18:50,970
 Let me listen. 

186
00:18:51,970 --> 00:18:54,370
 Who's outside? 

187
00:18:54,370 --> 00:18:55,450
 Don't you even recognize me? 

188
00:18:55,450 --> 00:18:57,650
 Are you my annoying dad? 

189
00:19:16,330 --> 00:19:19,610
 If not for that car accident years ago, 

190
00:19:20,970 --> 00:19:23,690
 I wouldn't have become like this. 

191
00:19:28,090 --> 00:19:30,610
 But it's too late for anything now. 

192
00:19:32,850 --> 00:19:39,290
Go. Pretend you never had a mother.

193
00:19:42,290 --> 00:19:44,410
Don't come see me again.

194
00:19:52,810 --> 00:19:54,720
Take care of yourself.

195
00:20:32,650 --> 00:20:34,720
Meng.

196
00:20:39,650 --> 00:20:41,536
Meng.

197
00:20:42,930 --> 00:20:44,800
Ye Meng.

198
00:20:45,730 --> 00:20:48,050
Meng.

199
00:20:48,050 --> 00:20:50,080
Ye Meng.

200
00:20:51,370 --> 00:20:53,344
Meng.

201
00:20:54,210 --> 00:20:55,210
Meng.

202
00:20:55,210 --> 00:20:57,216
Ye Meng.

203
00:20:59,610 --> 00:21:02,570
You're finally awake.
I was so scared these past few days.

204
00:21:07,610 --> 00:21:09,570
Feeling better?

205
00:21:09,570 --> 00:21:11,770
You didn't tell my grandmas, right?

206
00:21:11,770 --> 00:21:13,664
No one's been told.

207
00:21:15,770 --> 00:21:17,024
- Don't...
- Don't move yet.

208
00:21:17,024 --> 00:21:18,410
Raise the bed first.

209
00:21:18,410 --> 00:21:20,410
Slowly. Don't move.

210
00:21:20,410 --> 00:21:21,450
Ask her

211
00:21:21,450 --> 00:21:23,050
if there is any other discomfort.

212
00:21:23,050 --> 00:21:25,170
Meng, how are you?

213
00:21:25,170 --> 00:21:26,810
Where's Li Jin Yu?

214
00:21:26,810 --> 00:21:29,570
I haven't been able to reach him since discharge.

215
00:21:29,570 --> 00:21:31,370
You can't get through.

216
00:21:32,130 --> 00:21:33,810
Hand me my phone.

217
00:21:33,810 --> 00:21:37,792
Here.

218
00:21:52,050 --> 00:21:54,770
Stop overthinking. Rest.

219
00:21:54,770 --> 00:21:57,170
Rest. Don't dwell on things.

220
00:21:58,930 --> 00:22:00,810
Kai, go call the doctor.

221
00:22:19,850 --> 00:22:21,650
Go pick up Jia Yu?

222
00:22:23,170 --> 00:22:24,330
I don't need you to drive me there.

223
00:22:24,330 --> 00:22:27,250
I just came to talk with you.

224
00:22:28,170 --> 00:22:30,240
Okay.

225
00:22:31,890 --> 00:22:36,130
That day, I spoke too harshly.

226
00:22:36,130 --> 00:22:38,330
I was just caught up in anger.

227
00:22:38,330 --> 00:22:40,170
Please don't take it to heart.

228
00:22:41,250 --> 00:22:43,730
I'd forgotten until you mentioned it.

229
00:22:44,410 --> 00:22:48,210
He's your biological son after all. I understand.

230
00:23:00,610 --> 00:23:05,370
Kai, I admit I did feel attracted to you.

231
00:23:07,530 --> 00:23:12,650
But I just escaped an unhappy marriage.

232
00:23:13,370 --> 00:23:19,450
I'm not very confident about love now.

233
00:23:20,770 --> 00:23:23,930
Initially, I truly saw you as a younger brother.

234
00:23:24,570 --> 00:23:32,288
But you've been so good to me and Jia Yu.

235
00:23:33,290 --> 00:23:35,170
I'm deeply grateful.

236
00:23:38,810 --> 00:23:42,570
But I feel confused.

237
00:23:43,610 --> 00:23:45,536
And I don't have answers.

238
00:23:48,410 --> 00:23:52,850
And the relationship between us three...

239
00:23:54,410 --> 00:23:57,050
It's complicated now.

240
00:23:58,690 --> 00:24:02,930
Our situation has nothing to do with Ye Meng.

241
00:24:03,910 --> 00:24:06,130
I know it doesn't.

242
00:24:09,890 --> 00:24:12,610
But I can't stop overthinking.

243
00:24:17,810 --> 00:24:22,010
Could you give me some time?

244
00:24:22,010 --> 00:24:24,650
Let me sort myself out first.

245
00:24:56,170 --> 00:24:59,410
Li Jin Yu! Li Jin Yu!

246
00:25:06,490 --> 00:25:08,352
Li Jin Yu!

247
00:25:36,410 --> 00:25:41,810
 Ye Meng, no matter what happened
between Li Ling Bai and me, 

248
00:25:41,810 --> 00:25:45,450
 it's an unchangeable fact that she is my mother. 

249
00:25:47,170 --> 00:25:49,690
 Everything she did to your mother 

250
00:25:50,330 --> 00:25:52,970
 is beyond my lifetime's atonement. 

251
00:25:54,370 --> 00:25:56,650
 Upon reflection, 

252
00:25:56,650 --> 00:26:00,610
 all tragedies seem rooted in my existence. 

253
00:26:01,690 --> 00:26:05,010
 Too many suffered due to past events. 

254
00:26:05,010 --> 00:26:08,210
 I can't pretend nothing happened. 

255
00:26:12,570 --> 00:26:16,010
 Meeting you was my greatest fortune. 

256
00:26:16,010 --> 00:26:19,050
 I want you to stay carefree and happy 

257
00:26:19,050 --> 00:26:21,570
 instead of bearing these burdens with me. 

258
00:26:22,490 --> 00:26:25,050
 Please give me time 

259
00:26:25,050 --> 00:26:28,490
 to personally end all of this. 

260
00:26:58,770 --> 00:27:03,370
 
Dad, once

261
00:27:03,370 --> 00:27:06,410
you were my rock in this world.

262
00:27:08,490 --> 00:27:13,890
I never imagined I'd cause your demise.

263
00:27:17,890 --> 00:27:20,530
I've blamed myself relentlessly all these years.

264
00:27:24,770 --> 00:27:30,090
Meeting Ye Meng gave me hope to live again.

265
00:27:31,490 --> 00:27:36,930
 But now, I feel increasingly indebted to her, 

266
00:27:39,250 --> 00:27:42,570
 more than I can ever count. 

267
