268
00:28:35,332 --> 00:28:42,048
 

269
00:28:45,636 --> 00:28:48,832
 

270
00:28:53,970 --> 00:28:57,290
 
 Recently, Chairman Li X Bai of Hanhai Group 

271
00:28:57,290 --> 00:28:58,690
 was arrested for alleged illegal confinement, 

272
00:28:58,690 --> 00:29:00,330
 kidnapping, arson, 

273
00:29:00,330 --> 00:29:03,010
 and other criminal charges. 

274
00:29:03,010 --> 00:29:04,064
 The case also involves... 

275
00:29:04,064 --> 00:29:05,130
- Hello.
- Hello.

276
00:29:05,130 --> 00:29:06,290
Did anyone come by here earlier?

277
00:29:06,290 --> 00:29:09,770
A tall, thin man around 27-28 years old?

278
00:29:09,770 --> 00:29:11,250
Yes. He headed toward the back mountain.

279
00:29:11,250 --> 00:29:14,530
- I couldn't stop him.
-  Wang, Xu and others are caught. 

280
00:29:43,588 --> 00:29:48,864
 ♫ I still remember ♫ 

281
00:29:49,890 --> 00:29:51,690
Li Jin Yu!

282
00:29:52,420 --> 00:29:54,208
 ♫ With a sense of excitement ♫ 

283
00:29:54,208 --> 00:29:57,664
 ♫ You vowed eternal love ♫ 

284
00:29:57,664 --> 00:30:02,720
 ♫ But over time, you've forgotten ♫ 

285
00:30:06,570 --> 00:30:07,744
Li Jin Yu!

286
00:30:07,744 --> 00:30:11,584
 ♫ Only memories remain like scattered fireworks ♫ 

287
00:30:11,584 --> 00:30:15,170
 ♫ When I turned to walk away ♫ 

288
00:30:15,170 --> 00:30:17,970
Li Jin Yu! Li Jin Yu!

289
00:30:18,890 --> 00:30:20,370
What's wrong with you?

290
00:30:20,370 --> 00:30:21,930
Ignoring calls and messages.

291
00:30:21,930 --> 00:30:23,970
Writing about "ending all of this"?

292
00:30:23,970 --> 00:30:26,690
What are you planning to do? How?

293
00:30:27,970 --> 00:30:31,010
I was under investigation
with no access to my phone.

294
00:30:31,010 --> 00:30:35,210
And I couldn't find words to explain.

295
00:30:37,370 --> 00:30:39,250
So I wrote a letter.

296
00:30:44,610 --> 00:30:47,130
You exposed the flash drive's contents.

297
00:30:49,850 --> 00:30:53,970
I won't let your mother bear false accusations.

298
00:30:56,410 --> 00:31:01,770
Ye Meng, I won't run away this time.

299
00:31:02,490 --> 00:31:05,970
Do you know? I thought...

300
00:31:22,404 --> 00:31:27,076
 ♫ I cannot hide my feelings ♫ 

301
00:31:27,076 --> 00:31:30,080
 ♫ I'm about to be out of control ♫ 

302
00:31:30,730 --> 00:31:32,650
Grandma was right.

303
00:31:35,210 --> 00:31:37,170
People are like tea.

304
00:31:38,650 --> 00:31:43,490
New buds grow when spring arrives.

305
00:31:43,490 --> 00:31:46,090
So do humans.

306
00:31:46,090 --> 00:31:50,490
Where there's life, there's hope.

307
00:31:53,850 --> 00:31:57,810
Sorry for worrying you.

308
00:31:57,810 --> 00:32:00,992
 ♫ Even battered, I'll keep going ♫ 

309
00:32:00,992 --> 00:32:04,890
 ♫ The urge to run to you again ♫ 

310
00:32:04,890 --> 00:32:08,690
Ye Meng, thank you.

311
00:32:08,690 --> 00:32:10,720
And?

312
00:32:13,170 --> 00:32:15,072
I love you.

313
00:32:17,810 --> 00:32:19,776
I love you, too.

314
00:32:20,480 --> 00:32:22,496
 ♫ All I possess is drowned ♫ 

315
00:32:22,496 --> 00:32:25,824
 ♫ The me who still loves you deeply ♫ 

316
00:32:27,050 --> 00:32:28,960
Let's go home.

317
00:32:30,010 --> 00:32:31,930
I'm still angry.

318
00:32:34,410 --> 00:32:37,850
Wait. We'll go together.

319
00:32:37,850 --> 00:32:40,610
Do you know how long and rough this path is?

320
00:32:40,610 --> 00:32:42,490
I searched for you endlessly.

321
00:32:43,210 --> 00:32:45,850
Sorry. My fault.

322
00:32:45,850 --> 00:32:47,290
What will you do about it?

323
00:32:47,290 --> 00:32:50,010
Let me carry you down.

324
00:32:50,010 --> 00:32:52,770
No. What if you drop me?

325
00:32:53,410 --> 00:32:54,930
If you fall, I'll cushion your fall.

326
00:32:54,930 --> 00:32:56,570
- You think I don't know?
- Impossible.

327
00:32:56,570 --> 00:32:59,370
You'd toss me aside mid-fall.

328
00:33:01,252 --> 00:33:03,648
 

329
00:33:07,620 --> 00:33:10,450
 

330
00:33:10,450 --> 00:33:12,250
Everyone, please sit.

331
00:33:16,050 --> 00:33:21,450
I apologize for the negative impact
my family matters caused Hanhai.

332
00:33:21,450 --> 00:33:24,850
I formally apologize to all here.

333
00:33:31,210 --> 00:33:35,130
Everyone here is a veteran of our group.

334
00:33:35,130 --> 00:33:40,450
Hanhai's achievements over the years
are built on your hard work and dedication.

335
00:33:40,450 --> 00:33:42,450
I believe you've all heard

336
00:33:42,450 --> 00:33:47,370
about the news related to the predecessor
of Hailan Bay, the Tianhui Garden project.

337
00:33:47,370 --> 00:33:51,250
As Hanhai's largest shareholder,

338
00:33:51,250 --> 00:33:56,050
I will take full personal responsibility
for the recent negative publicity.

339
00:33:56,050 --> 00:34:00,210
So I'll allocate the net profits from my shares

340
00:34:00,210 --> 00:34:05,610
to compensate victims and their families
affected by the previous financial fraud.

341
00:34:05,610 --> 00:34:10,570
More qualified professionals
will manage the company in the future.

342
00:34:13,250 --> 00:34:15,730
I only have one demand.

343
00:34:15,730 --> 00:34:18,130
Phase III of the Hailan Bay

344
00:34:18,130 --> 00:34:21,250
must preserve the original appearance
of the coastal village.

345
00:34:43,410 --> 00:34:45,290
No more playing CEO?

346
00:34:45,290 --> 00:34:47,130
I'm never cut out for this role.

347
00:34:47,130 --> 00:34:50,610
I better go back to accounting certifications.

348
00:34:50,610 --> 00:34:53,210
Let us small-town folks not make
a mess here anymore.

349
00:34:53,210 --> 00:34:55,810
Stay another night or leave tomorrow?

350
00:34:55,810 --> 00:34:57,290
Let's head straight home.

351
00:34:57,290 --> 00:35:00,050
Perfect timing for Kai's restaurant opening.

352
00:35:00,050 --> 00:35:02,050
- Let's go.
- Go.

353
00:35:04,516 --> 00:35:09,344
 

354
00:35:11,170 --> 00:35:12,290
Thank you.

355
00:35:12,290 --> 00:35:14,912
Mr. Cheng, the time has come for ribbon-cutting.

356
00:35:14,912 --> 00:35:16,090
Come on.

357
00:35:16,090 --> 00:35:17,130
- Come on.
- Come on.

358
00:35:17,130 --> 00:35:20,650
Three, two, one!

359
00:35:20,650 --> 00:35:23,330
Grand opening!

360
00:35:24,890 --> 00:35:29,650
Thanks to all loyal customers
for your continuous support of Jubaoshi.

361
00:35:29,650 --> 00:35:33,730
Today marks Jubaoshi Restaurant's opening day.

362
00:35:33,730 --> 00:35:36,170
For celebration, 20% off the entire menu.

363
00:35:36,170 --> 00:35:40,730
All membership card holders
get free lottery entries.

364
00:35:40,730 --> 00:35:42,610
I checked the grand prize myself.

365
00:35:42,610 --> 00:35:44,490
Mr. Cheng really opened his wallet this time.

366
00:35:44,490 --> 00:35:45,570
What are you waiting for?

367
00:35:45,570 --> 00:35:46,970
Hurry up, first come, first served!

368
00:35:46,970 --> 00:35:48,210
Come in, please.

369
00:35:48,210 --> 00:35:49,730
Hurry inside now. Come on!

370
00:35:49,730 --> 00:35:52,010
- Come.
- Go.

371
00:35:52,010 --> 00:35:54,210
So crowded.

372
00:35:54,210 --> 00:35:56,010
Booming.

373
00:36:04,690 --> 00:36:06,890
Stop looking and waiting.

374
00:36:06,890 --> 00:36:09,810
Ya En took Jia Yu to a city event.

375
00:36:09,810 --> 00:36:11,968
But they sent flower baskets.

376
00:36:18,690 --> 00:36:20,330
It's fine.

377
00:36:20,330 --> 00:36:22,690
I'm okay. She might show up later.

378
00:36:22,690 --> 00:36:24,650
Get in, come on!

379
00:36:33,152 --> 00:36:40,864
 

380
00:36:42,450 --> 00:36:45,570
Any feedback on the dishes?

381
00:36:45,570 --> 00:36:47,450
- No, great.
- Everything's good?

382
00:36:47,450 --> 00:36:50,810
Okay, promote us on social media.

383
00:36:50,810 --> 00:36:52,010
Bring friends next time.

384
00:36:52,010 --> 00:36:53,056
- Okay.
- Okay.

385
00:36:53,056 --> 00:36:54,090
- Bye.
- Bye.

386
00:36:54,090 --> 00:36:55,136
Bye.

387
00:36:55,136 --> 00:36:57,970
Kai, come check this.

388
00:36:57,970 --> 00:36:59,968
Why hasn't he arrived yet?

389
00:36:59,968 --> 00:37:01,010
I'm getting nervous.

390
00:37:01,010 --> 00:37:02,756
No idea.

391
00:37:02,756 --> 00:37:04,370
 

392
00:37:04,370 --> 00:37:05,690
Mall shopping maybe?

393
00:37:05,690 --> 00:37:07,810
 
Okay, let's shop for clothes.

394
00:37:10,810 --> 00:37:15,410
Turning a bar into a restaurant? What a joke.

395
00:37:15,410 --> 00:37:17,570
Tai Ming Xiao.

396
00:37:17,570 --> 00:37:18,810
Welcome.

397
00:37:18,810 --> 00:37:20,640
Tai Ming...

398
00:37:26,490 --> 00:37:29,890
What? The new Three Musketeers?

399
00:37:31,490 --> 00:37:35,330
We need to tell you something.

400
00:37:41,410 --> 00:37:43,296
Sorry.

401
00:37:45,890 --> 00:37:47,744
What's this about?

402
00:37:48,930 --> 00:37:52,210
Mr. Gou, here for my opening day?

403
00:37:57,888 --> 00:37:59,840
No.

404
00:38:07,010 --> 00:38:09,210
True gangster style.

405
00:38:09,210 --> 00:38:11,490
Name his price.

406
00:38:11,490 --> 00:38:13,312
I'll double it.

407
00:38:14,240 --> 00:38:16,050
No.

408
00:38:16,050 --> 00:38:18,450
He's still in the dark?

409
00:38:20,530 --> 00:38:24,090
If you're burning cash, give it to me.

410
00:38:24,090 --> 00:38:25,610
I'll give you shares.

411
00:38:25,610 --> 00:38:28,930
Forget money. This isn't about money.

412
00:38:30,290 --> 00:38:34,930
The truth is that I'm Ye Meng's husband.

413
00:38:38,090 --> 00:38:40,000
You think I'll buy that?

414
00:38:41,490 --> 00:38:43,370
Let her go first.

415
00:38:43,370 --> 00:38:45,280
What are you doing?

416
00:38:47,392 --> 00:38:49,344
Look.

417
00:38:51,716 --> 00:38:53,920
 

418
00:38:59,010 --> 00:39:01,410
Believe it now? Convinced?

419
00:39:13,090 --> 00:39:14,930
Did I return from abroad just now?

420
00:39:22,090 --> 00:39:24,170
You've all truly disappointed me.

421
00:39:27,610 --> 00:39:29,050
Let me talk to him.

422
00:39:29,050 --> 00:39:30,944
Hurry up.

423
00:39:31,770 --> 00:39:33,730
I think he's crying.

424
00:39:33,730 --> 00:39:37,090
Genuinely heartbroken this time.

425
00:39:37,090 --> 00:39:38,890
What can we do?

426
00:39:40,050 --> 00:39:42,048
I feel bad for him.

427
00:40:05,690 --> 00:40:07,610
Enough already.

428
00:40:07,610 --> 00:40:09,530
Still staring at the ocean?

429
00:40:16,330 --> 00:40:18,970
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

430
00:40:18,970 --> 00:40:23,690
The situation required secrecy to protect Ye Meng.

431
00:40:23,690 --> 00:40:25,290
You always assume you're right

432
00:40:25,290 --> 00:40:27,210
and hide everything from me.

433
00:40:27,210 --> 00:40:30,370
You married secretly
and quit the competition secretly.

434
00:40:32,210 --> 00:40:34,490
That competition wasn't just about you.

435
00:40:34,490 --> 00:40:36,490
I gave my all, too.

436
00:40:38,330 --> 00:40:40,384
I know.

437
00:40:41,090 --> 00:40:43,690
It was my fault
that you lost the competition back then.

438
00:40:43,690 --> 00:40:45,810
I owe you an apology.

439
00:40:45,810 --> 00:40:49,010
My anger wasn't about losing the competition,

440
00:40:49,010 --> 00:40:51,890
but because you left without a word.

441
00:40:51,890 --> 00:40:55,890
I considered you a brother.
What did you take me for?

442
00:41:04,810 --> 00:41:08,770
Actually, my father passed away back then.

443
00:41:13,770 --> 00:41:15,930
I kept wanting to tell you all

444
00:41:15,930 --> 00:41:18,210
but didn't know how to bring it up.

445
00:41:19,090 --> 00:41:21,330
You know me.

446
00:41:21,330 --> 00:41:25,690
Always closed off,
keeping everyone at arm's length.

447
00:41:25,690 --> 00:41:29,330
The only person
I could truly open up to was my dad.

448
00:41:29,330 --> 00:41:33,290
But my dad died in a car accident because of me.

449
00:41:34,210 --> 00:41:37,090
I couldn't possibly compete back then.

450
00:41:37,090 --> 00:41:39,210
I became completely withdrawn.

451
00:41:39,890 --> 00:41:43,770
Then I cut all ties and hid from everyone.

452
00:41:48,330 --> 00:41:52,210
I thought that'd be the rest of my life

453
00:41:53,090 --> 00:41:55,090
until Ye Meng came into my life.

454
00:41:55,090 --> 00:41:58,730
She brought new vitality to me.

455
00:42:00,290 --> 00:42:06,770
That's why I can stand here
saying this to you now.

456
00:42:06,770 --> 00:42:09,610
I'm truly sorry for keeping this from you.

457
00:42:09,610 --> 00:42:15,530
But in my heart, I treasure the time we shared.

458
00:42:15,530 --> 00:42:18,490
You've always been my closest buddy in my eyes.

459
00:42:25,344 --> 00:42:27,610
I'm sorry

460
00:42:27,610 --> 00:42:31,250
for the things about Ye Meng
and what happened back then.

461
00:43:19,812 --> 00:43:22,084
 ♫ You ♫ 

462
00:43:22,084 --> 00:43:24,260
 ♫ The moment I see you ♫ 

463
00:43:25,156 --> 00:43:27,475
 ♫ The moment I think of you ♫ 

464
00:43:28,292 --> 00:43:34,276
 ♫ The moment I hear any news of you ♫ 

465
00:43:34,276 --> 00:43:40,196
 ♫ My heart is touched ♫ 

466
00:43:40,196 --> 00:43:44,356
 ♫ My mind is occupied ♫ 

467
00:43:44,356 --> 00:43:46,820
 ♫ Go ♫ 

468
00:43:46,820 --> 00:43:48,836
 ♫ Where to go ♫ 

469
00:43:48,836 --> 00:43:52,964
 ♫ How to escape ♫ 

470
00:43:52,964 --> 00:43:58,948
 ♫ Those memories of you ♫ 

471
00:43:58,948 --> 00:44:02,916
 ♫ Have drowned me ♫ 

472
00:44:02,916 --> 00:44:08,932
 ♫ I can't let go ♫ 

473
00:44:10,180 --> 00:44:13,252
 ♫ I remain silent ♫ 

474
00:44:13,252 --> 00:44:16,836
 ♫ My words stuck in my throat ♫ 

475
00:44:16,836 --> 00:44:22,916
 ♫ Maybe this'll end the sorrow ♫ 

476
00:44:22,916 --> 00:44:27,677
 ♫ Pretending to be determined ♫ 

477
00:44:27,677 --> 00:44:32,924
 ♫ I'm still trapped at the starting point ♫ 

478
00:44:34,826 --> 00:44:37,761
 ♫ The most perfect lie ♫ 

479
00:44:37,761 --> 00:44:40,717
 ♫ I even deceive myself ♫ 

480
00:44:40,717 --> 00:44:42,884
 ♫ If love means letting go ♫ 

481
00:44:42,884 --> 00:44:47,684
 ♫ Let's sever all connections ♫ 

482
00:44:47,684 --> 00:44:49,828
 ♫ But why ♫ 

483
00:44:49,828 --> 00:44:53,348
 ♫ The moment tears fall ♫ 

484
00:44:53,348 --> 00:44:58,401
 ♫ I don't want you to leave ♫ 

